sellerCard.oneLiner: Professional Wix, WordPress, Webflow Website Designer and Developer
sellerCard.description: Hi, I am an expert and highly experienced web designer. I have been creating websites for over 5 years, so I know all the intricacies of website design from domain registration to customization in Shopify, Wix, WordPress, Webflow, Squarespace, GoDaddy, and other CMS platforms. I can design your website from scratch or redesign the existing one to acceptable modern standards. I can create a custom website to your liking, and make changes based on your requirements. I'll optimize your online store for mobile and desktop to make an impact online.

description.content:
Hi Fiverr Community,


Are you looking for an experienced Webflow expert who can design and develop a stunning Webflow website for you that reflects your brand's personality and captivates your visitors?


Look no further! Here I am.


As a Webflow developer with 5+ years of experience, I have the skills and expertise to create beautiful, responsive, and user-friendly sites that exceed your expectations. I will do custom design or convert your Figma to Webflow design websites that are optimized for conversion and built to scale.


I specialize in designing websites for businesses, startups, and individuals who want to showcase their brands in a unique and professional way.


What I Offer:


  • Responsive Webflow Site
  • ️Pixel Perfect Design
  • Figma to Webflow Conversion
  • ️Attractive Landing Pages Design
  • ️Fully Responsive on Mobile, Tab & Desktop
  • ️Advanced Animations
  • Visually Attractive Color Combination
  • ️SEO Optimization


Why Me?


  • Quick and Professional
  • 24/7 Available
  • ️Unlimited Revisions
  • ️30 Days of Ongoing Support


Take a smart decision! Just place an order to get premium services. Let's work together to take your site to the next level.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you fix a bug in my Webflow website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. I can fix bugs from your Webflow website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will the website be responsive across all devices?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! It will be responsive across all devices and browsers.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you convert Figma, xd and sketch design into Webflow?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, as a developer, I have been working on developing websites in Webflow. If you need to convert your design files into Webflow kindly inbox me.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer help after project completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I totally do that with all my clients. Should you find yourself in a pickle after the project is complete, I can offer some guidance.

reviews.comment: I’ve hired Akibur on several projects to date and will continue to use him. He is incredibly responsive (even in the late hours for him), and his attention to detail, problem-solving skills, knowledge of Webflow, and overall professionalism are excellent,

Akibur is phenomenal. He created an awesome website for me and made all the edits I asked without hesitation. He is professional and does not give up. We had issues integrating my video and he figured it out. I would highly recommend. My site is wonderful; studiokasa.art

seller_response.comment: Very professional and polite. It's a pleasure working with you. Looking towards the upcoming projects!

reviews.comment: The experience was professional in communication. We had an overall positive experience and would work with them again. I would have appreciated more attention to detail but they were acceptable and took feedback very well.

seller_response.comment:
Thank you for your valuable feedback.

I'd love to assist you with more projects.

reviews.comment:
Very happy working with him.
He is very kind and try to complete all the requests that I asked. 
Later, I have a plan to build another website.
I'm sure that I will ask him to do that in the future.

seller_response.comment: Thank you for your kind words. I look forward to working with you again in the future.

reviews.comment: We worked with Akib for the second time. Unfortunately, there were a few more communication problems this time. Perhaps our expectations were also very high. In any case, he went to a lot of trouble and was also very cooperative in finding a solution.
